*Haberland, H. &amp; Mortensen, J. (2016) Transcription as second order entextualisation: The challenge of heteroglossia. In: Capone, A. &amp; Mey, J. L. (eds.): Interdisciplinary Studies in Pragmatics, Culture and Society, 581–600. Cham: Springer.
